"xesti√≥n e aos procesos: como poden traballar produtivamente en "
"colaboraci√≥n as estruturas de mando xer√°rquico das corporaci√≥ns e as "
"comunidades semi-descentralizadas de voluntarios? Coincidir√°n no "
"significado de \"produtivamente\"?"

#. Tag: para
#: ch05.xml:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Financial backing is, in general, welcomed by open source development "
"communities. It can reduce a project's vulnerability to the Forces of Chaos, "
"which sweep away so many projects before they really get off the ground, and "
"therefore it can make people more willing to give the software a "
"chance&mdash;they feel they're investing their time into something that will "
"still be around six months from now. After all, credibility is contagious, "
"to a point. When, say, IBM backs an open source project, people pretty much "
"assume the project won't be allowed to fail, and their resultant willingness "
"to devote effort to it can make that a self-fulfilling prophecy."
msgstr ""
