"\"/></phrase> para saber m√°is sobre eles."

#. Tag: title
#: ch05.xml:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Be Open About Your Motivations"
msgstr "S√© Aberto Sobre as T√∫as Motivaci√≥ns"

#. Tag: para
#: ch05.xml:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be as open about your organization's goals as you can without compromising "
