"cliente, pero en todo caso, el non vive do contrato. Remarca que s√≥ √© un "
"adorno √≥s debates t√©cnico sobre como facer as cousas."

#. Tag: para
#: ch05.xml:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That example shows another reason why it's good to be open about contracts. "
"There may be multiple organizations sponsoring contracts on a given open "
