#. Tag: title
#: ch05.xml:753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case study: the CVS password-authentication protocol"
msgstr "Caso de estudo: o protocolo de autenticaci√≥n v√≠a contrasinal de CVS"

#. Tag: para
#: ch05.xml:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In 1995, I was one half of a partnership that provided support and "
"enhancements for CVS (the Concurrent Versions System; see <ulink url="
"\"http://www.cvshome.org/\"></ulink>). My partner Jim and I were, "
"informally, the maintainers of CVS by that point. But we'd never thought "
